originalText.text: Best OBGYN experience Ihave ever had!!  Such a great meeting with Dr. Justine Kim. Dr. Kim is absolutely best! best! best! and was extremely thorough and very patient in her explanations. She was very understanding about all of my concerns! The staff was very polite, the office is very beautiful, clean and spacious. Would highly recommend!

originalText.text: My gynecologist announced she was retiring - which put me in a panic.  If you find a good doctor and bond forms & they are not easily replaced.  So I arrived at Westside OBGYN nervous & sad.  Dr. Kim was kind, a good listener, and thorough.  I don't think she knows how UPLIFTING my office visit with her was, but it was.  I'm delighted to have found her.

originalText.text: Dr Kim is a wonderful doctor!  She does very thorough exams, always communications what she is doing and why and allows as much time as needed to respond to any questions or concerns.  Plus, if a test comes back negative, she calls immediately to explain the ramifications and next steps.  I'm thrilled to have her as my gynecologist!

originalText.text: Dr. Kim is literally one of the best OB GYN’s I’ve ever had. Feelings seen and heard by a practitioner is rare. Dr. Kim listens thoroughly to my concerns and responds in ways that does not make me feel judged at all. No question is “too small”. Talking about Zodiacs during my exams, makes the time fly bye lol. I would give her 10 stars if I could!
